                    "name": "Treasure and Rewards",
                    "image": "Sidebar_5_TreasureAndRewards.png"
                },
                "html": "While viper vine pollen degrades quickly after it is harvested carefully from the plant, a character who has a set of alchemical tools can gather and preserve 1d6 doses of pollen with a successful DC 33 <a aonid=\"4\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Crafting</a> or <a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Nature</a> check and 10 minutes of work. A single dose of viper vine pollen is worth 300 gp as raw materials for crafting any alchemical or magical item that creates an <a aonid=\"93\" game-obj=\"Traits\">incapacitation</a> effect."
            }
        ],
